OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrugs plan aims to help    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F300,000 problem drug users 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government says it is to provide   
OL,6, rehabilitation for 300,000 drug users  
OL,7, who carry out half of all shop thefts, 
OL,8, robberies and burglaries.              
OL,10,FMinisters have announced that a 10-year
OL,11,Fdrugs strategy will allocate #780m in  
OL,12,Ffunding for the drug treatment system  
OL,13,Fin England.                            
OL,15,FIt also includes #300m for combating   
OL,16,Fmore than 2,000 county lines gangs.    
OL,18,FThe government says that in some cases 
OL,19,Fcasual drug users may lose their       
OL,20,Fdriving licences or passports.         
